casebody.head_matter:
Hunter R. LEVI, petitioner,
v.
Thomas E. PEREZ, Secretary of Labor, et al.
No. 15-5923.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 2, 2015.
Motion of petitioner for leave in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
